&lt;p>众所周知，设置 matplotlib 输出中文需要：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>plt&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>rcParams[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;font.sans-serif&amp;#39;&lt;/span>]&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;SimHei&amp;#39;&lt;/span>] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 用来正常显示中文标签&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>plt&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>rcParams[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;axes.unicode_minus&amp;#39;&lt;/span>]&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">False&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 用来正常显示负号&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>